OL,3,CJersey church transformed into
OL,4,Cimmersive soundscape
OL,6,FJersey's St Helier Town Church has
OL,7,Fbeen transformed into an immersive
OL,8,Fsoundscape by ArtHouse Jersey for the
OL,9,Fnext two weeks.
OL,11,FArtHouse Jersey's The Sound of Colour,
OL,12,FArrivals, tells the story of the
OL,13,Femergence of language in Jersey.
OL,15,FThis is shown through projection
OL,16,Fmapping onto the church ceiling.
OL,18,FWhile watching the projections,
OL,19,Fspecial audio recordings can be heard
OL,20,Fwith a different track for each
OL,21,Fchapter.
