OL,6,FArthouse Jersey Producer Natasha
OL,7,FDettman said: "You will follow a
OL,8,Fjourney through time right back from
OL,9,Fthe Magdalenian times, the late Stone
OL,10,FAge, through the Iron Age and Viking
OL,11,Finvaders, as well as the Norman times.
OL,13,F"This continues right up until the
OL,14,Fpresent day.
OL,16,F"In each of those chapters, you will
OL,17,Fhear some of the languages that were
OL,18,Fspoken.
