OL,6,F"This exhibition really is for
OL,7,Feveryone. You can come and join the
OL,8,Fexhibition at any point, it is on a
OL,9,Floop.
OL,11,F"Children are free to run around, lie
OL,12,Fon the floor - it is very informal."
OL,14,FOn 16 November people also have the
OL,15,Fopportunity to see The Sound of Colour
OL,16,F: Origins which was shown back in 2021
OL,17,Fwhich explores patterns found in
OL,18,Fnature.
OL,20,FIt is free to enter the exhibition and
OL,21,Fwill run until 23 November.
